{"tid":335530,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"6年前領養左隻poodle，有冇比人呃？","createTime":"2017-07-25T15:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T16:59:24.000Z","uid":14100,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5d5e6dc95832d1bd9f2f39acd245c052fe6d165e","tid":335530,"uid":14100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:39:56.000Z","msg":"首先講明,我唔係想買,亦唔係賣狗,我一向支持領養<br />\n<br />\n事源係咁，6年前，我想領養狗狗，但因為住私樓，所以要家訪果d咩就已經收哂皮<br />\n<br />\n結果我上網見到有1個月大cream色標準貴婦bb可以<span style=\"color: blue;\">領養</span><br />\n(佢聲稱話一胎生左太多)<br />\n<br />\n但同佢講時，佢話要收返$2800，但佢會俾哂d物資我(包括一個品質幾靚嘅狗袋，bb糧，成犬糧，狗色bb衫幾件，玩具幾件，狗繩等，同埋唔記得有冇bb奶)<br />\n<br />\n依家我只係諗返起，想知其實真係領養定賣狗<br />\n(當時根本冇為意係咩品種狗，只要唔係玩到超大隻就ok，後來醫生話佢係屬於純種的標準貴婦狗)<br />\n<br />\n我又唔知岀面通常賣幾錢<br />\n同埋聽過人講其實領養係會俾封利是仔對方<br />\n<br />\nsor for 1999<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以講返俾我知實情係點？<br />\n<br />\n利申: 有冇比人昆都冇所謂，都會繼續錫爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ad26401901224f1cf1348d46ecc69c7e8ae1b0","tid":335530,"uid":12944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:41:34.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"4e55393ac22376ac10e9918faa950670cbe72acb","tid":335530,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:45:29.000Z","msg":"要錢已經係俾人屈"},{"pid":"d9879c82398a5c09b3890af3e95c008078817ebb","tid":335530,"uid":14100,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:52:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>圖呢</blockquote><br />\n唔放啦，實在太多fd上連登，毒撚唔想比人認到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2848183e81cf3876d75bafe167aaee9b030e84c1","tid":335530,"uid":14100,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:56:28.000Z","msg":"諗諗下，行得正企得正，比人認到其實冇乜所謂<br />\n跟返規矩補返張圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zht5yejs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzht5yejs&h=c1f8e84a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bfc043f5082f4560155b190f1856849d43a0f94c","tid":335530,"uid":125382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:58:09.000Z","msg":"比左錢就係買啦...唔通當互捐呀?<br />\n佢捐隻狗俾你 你捐番啲錢俾佢咁?"},{"pid":"03f2ccde301b3bcc7b50b0f33688ce8cec67b54e","tid":335530,"uid":8167,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T16:15:22.000Z","msg":"你6年前啲野 依家先講"},{"pid":"01192224a2adfd3aabd4494a9d01b4e26fe44267","tid":335530,"uid":4392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T16:18:18.000Z","msg":"6年前而家先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n想當年我都係&quot;領養&quot; 要我比番針錢 好似一共8百幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293f2200dc9fe4d36284de7da2192a5c44ba9bdf","tid":335530,"uid":7049,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T17:02:49.000Z","msg":"公屋又唔比領養 居屋又唔比領養 私樓都唔比領養<br />\n咁係咪訓街先比領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a18f560ddd5e5827d48d7c7d561f89da8a8857","tid":335530,"uid":21638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T03:30:54.000Z","msg":"佢都有心賣狗啦講真<br />\n不過比寵物店平咋嘛<br />\n<br />\n無所謂啦<br />\n<br />\n我上試過係狗場救狗佢都收我4k<br />\n合眼緣同埋真心想養我當做善事囉"},{"pid":"db47f9f0a71ab0cef62f47628773452780fc8f05","tid":335530,"uid":14100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:52:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢都有心賣狗啦講真<br />\n不過比寵物店平咋嘛<br />\n<br />\n無所謂啦<br />\n<br />\n我上試過係狗場救狗佢都收我4k<br />\n合眼緣同埋真心想養我當做善事囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係合眼緣，我老母一睇到就好鐘意佢"},{"pid":"41dd8b7e960161b720b79be543652d04f8533af7","tid":335530,"uid":29423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:57:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>6年前而家先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n想當年我都係&quot;領養&quot; 要我比番針錢 好似一共8百幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n八百幾都合理嘅"},{"pid":"113fce066171c32d555612cc02c610ac3e05035f","tid":335530,"uid":27234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:09:21.000Z","msg":"純種貴婦<br />\n仲要BB<br />\n養左六年都生勾勾冇病冇痛<br />\n剩係d物資都起碼值$500-$800<br />\n$2800真係抵到爛"},{"pid":"d34c99c64b9369409b1058171c9dd1f097126a09","tid":335530,"uid":8103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T05:15:27.000Z","msg":"標準貴婦好大隻架喎？你個隻應該叫玩具貴婦<br />\n<br />\n你想知佢係咪呃人領養 實質賣狗？<br />\n你知唔知佢之後仲有冇咁做先？<br />\n如果冇，係佢隻狗生啲狗bb出黎，又比咁多物資你<br />\n收返少少錢都有道理喎，二千八算平啦<br />\n你地又三唔識七，你仲要隔六年先諗呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做乜9<br />\n<br />\n如果佢自家繁殖賣狗就另計啦<br />\n你有冇證據先"},{"pid":"a22a841327e2fd8bd5c2a1537673ab5321c1a66c","tid":335530,"uid":8103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T05:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/27/131749_3b60f2a75eec45e366696b6debd55cbb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F27%2F131749_3b60f2a75eec45e366696b6debd55cbb.jpg&h=bcb05ee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n標準貴婦狗"},{"pid":"4022fa2402f12ce1431530f95e55c776191075d2","tid":335530,"uid":30377,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T05:20:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/27/131749_3b60f2a75eec45e366696b6debd55cbb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F27%2F131749_3b60f2a75eec45e366696b6debd55cbb.jpg&h=bcb05ee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n標準貴婦狗</blockquote><br />\n成碌鳩咁貴婦鳩渣話?"},{"pid":"34ab9fe0488be9ad66f2c1fd2bd5d9de5d8b8ade","tid":335530,"uid":64535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T16:59:24.000Z","msg":"樓主 唔似標準 最多迷你貴婦 都係個句啦 你比個家佢 係緣份 好好照顧佢<br />\n<br />\n利申：有隻8歲貴婦"}]}